movie.title: Occurrence at Mills Creek
movie.description_intro: Struggling with the guilt of her sister's accidental death, Clara soon begins to succumb to the same strange occurrences that have haunted her family for generations as she uncovers the unsettling truth about her lineage and its dark legacy.

movies.title: Can't Hardly Wait
movies.summary: It's high school graduation and, like all seniors, they want to party. So, 500 high school seniors look forward to a party while, in the meantime, a boy wants to get a girl he's loved for years who just broke up with her boyfriend, and one head-case who wants revenge on a lifelong bully. So, the party comes, things develop. People have sex, drink, and go along with most of the guidelines of a high school graduation party.

movies.title: Yamaguchi-gumi gaiden: Kyushu shinko-sakusen
movies.summary: Through a simple act of revenge, Tokyo's deadliest assassin sets off the biggest gang war in crime history. And there is nowhere to hide when the most vicious criminals imaginable try to hunt him down, determined to annihilate the definitive master of death

movies.title: The Dreamers
movies.summary: Paris, spring 1968. While most students take the lead in the May 'revolution', a French poet's twin son Theo and daughter Isabelle enjoy the good life in his grand Paris home. As film buffs they meet and 'adopt' modest, conservatively educated Californian student Matthew. With their parents away for a month, they drag him into an orgy of indulgence of all senses, losing all of his and the last of their innocence. A sexual threesome shakes their rapport, yet only the outside reality will break it up.
